data.title: Contributions to the tribute of Joseph D. Henderson
data.meta_description: Contributions to the tribute of Joseph  D. Henderson.
data.text:
K

Karine Fages from France lit a candle

//s3.amazonaws.com/skins.funeraltechweb.com/tribute-gestures/Candle2.png

I am saddened to hear of Joe's passing away. All the way from France and despite the years, I have many fond memories of his impeccable dedication to the Rotary Youth Exchange. I was lucky enough to be a part of the programm in 1993/1994 and I have never forgotten Joe's generosity and constant attention. Please extend my condolences and my deepest sympathies for their loss to his family.

R

Russ and Barb Byers posted a condolence

We consider it a great honor to have known Joe. He was a true gentleman. We are sorry we are away from home and won't be able to attend the memorial but please know you are in our thoughts and prayers.
